title: pâte brisée recipe
description: good & simple pie crust
---
§recipe
	§ingredients
		250g flour
		125g butter
		1dl water
		4g salt
	§/ingredients

	§instructions
		mix the flour with butter chunks until its like sand but not too much so that the buter melts
		add the water with salt dissolved inside
		mix it so that its like evenly mixed
		put the dough on a table and kinda crush it against the surface with ur palm
		leave it to rest for at least 2 hours
		u can roll it out or put it in the fridge (with plastic film so it dont dry out)
	§/instructions
§/recipe
